<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
   
    <title>AI Kiosk - 모드 선택</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 100px;
        }
        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px; /* 버튼 사이 간격 */
        }
        .mode-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .mode-label {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .mode-button {
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            font-size: 28px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            color: white;
        }
        .mode-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .latest-mode {
            background-color: skyblue;
        }
        .quick-mode {
            background-color: orange;
        }
    </style>
    
</head>
<body>
    <h1>모드를 선택하세요</h1>
    <br><br>

    <div class="button-container">
        <div class="mode-wrapper">
            <div class="mode-label">단골이신가요?</div>
            <form action="/latest_mode" method="get">
                <button class="mode-button latest-mode" type="submit">🕒최신조회 모드</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="mode-wrapper">
            <div class="mode-label">기본 조회</div>
            <form action="/quick_mode" method="get">
                <button class="mode-button quick-mode" type="submit">✅퀵조회 모드</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
